name: 2011-noaa-ortho-rectified-mosaic-of-merrimack-river-and-plum-island-sound-massachusetts-mean-lo
notes: This data set contains ortho-rectified mosaic tiles, created as a product from the NOAA Integrated Ocean and Coastal Mapping (IOCM) initiative. The source imagery was acquired from 20110619 - 20110619. The images were acquired with an Applanix Digital Sensor System (DSS). The original images were acquired at a higher resolution than the final ortho-rectified mosaic.
